{"tid":2252973,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"我真係好撚鐘意香港呀","createTime":"2020-10-22T00:26:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T04:22:55.000Z","uid":380895,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2991e5048580d49ed83416f6674df586f764ae86","tid":2252973,"uid":380895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T00:26:39.000Z","msg":"其實你鐘意呢度乜9？<br />\n<br />\n住：<br />\n成千萬先買到個正常少少既兩房屋苑單位<br />\n幾百萬上車盤殘到狗屎咁<br />\n公居俾晒癈老新移民<br />\n<br />\n人工：<br />\n打份牛工得個兩三萬<br />\n交左租供左樓得返雞碎咁多<br />\n<br />\n交通：<br />\n係呀係好方便<br />\n但係周圍都多人到PK<br />\n基本上非繁忙時間都好撚多人坐地鐵巴士<br />\n想揸架車，泊車都成幾千蚊一個月<br />\n想帶小朋友或者條女去個郊遊既話，冇車真係唔撚想去<br />\n<br />\n人：<br />\n香港人本性就係仆街自私搵錢至上<br />\n睇下國泰空姐post 就知道<br />\n就得抗爭個時有共同敵人先有少少團結<br />\n但都有好撚多人覺得你阻住佢返工<br />\n平時係街都係好多人冇禮貌,服務業嘅多數西口西面<br />\n<br />\n教育：<br />\n唔撚駛講啦屌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實講得出 我真係好撚鐘意香港呀 呢句野，係鐘意咩？ 定係只係覺得生活左咁多年，所以呢度一定好？？"},{"pid":"26eb7bde03e3bff81dbe40a128d7e9ceb86172ca","tid":2252973,"uid":9466,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T00:27:48.000Z","msg":"因為呢度係我屋企"},{"pid":"49dea8befd18e0587ed50bae53c59a3e15b41453","tid":2252973,"uid":302151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26eb7bde03e3bff81dbe40a128d7e9ceb86172ca","tid":2252973,"uid":9466,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T00:27:48.000Z","msg":"因為呢度係我屋企"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T00:30:35.000Z","msg":"駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b76e34dc5bf27f872240928d717da7558b1c02d9","tid":2252973,"uid":362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T00:33:16.000Z","msg":"好鐘意十幾年前香港. 現在越來越差"},{"pid":"a29deda328f22e41268a84df758ab485004a6b71","tid":2252973,"uid":22310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T01:01:57.000Z","msg":"鍾意香港人，鍾意廣東話<br />\n呢個地方有問題，唔係應該解決呢啲問題？"},{"pid":"d2239d69202a499fe5fe641c8f9b0691012b151b","tid":2252973,"uid":140726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T01:31:00.000Z","msg":"我唔撚鐘意<br />\n咁可以點？輪到我揀咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1fb4f0e2b140a9ba4154068b1bf3e312934e088","tid":2252973,"uid":380895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"26eb7bde03e3bff81dbe40a128d7e9ceb86172ca","tid":2252973,"uid":9466,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T00:27:48.000Z","msg":"因為呢度係我屋企"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T01:58:06.000Z","msg":"屋企就一定要鐘意？"},{"pid":"c4a25796414202d4f41776a7985cee435179230e","tid":2252973,"uid":380895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a29deda328f22e41268a84df758ab485004a6b71","tid":2252973,"uid":22310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T01:01:57.000Z","msg":"鍾意香港人，鍾意廣東話<br />\n呢個地方有問題，唔係應該解決呢啲問題？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T01:59:39.000Z","msg":"鐘意廣東話都唔一定係度生活架<br />\n解決問題，但有能力解決咩？到頭來得返無力感"},{"pid":"7f8f67e29da6a3bb0ca77ac85419a798ed85075a","tid":2252973,"uid":380895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2239d69202a499fe5fe641c8f9b0691012b151b","tid":2252973,"uid":140726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T01:31:00.000Z","msg":"我唔撚鐘意<br />\n咁可以點？輪到我揀咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T02:00:21.000Z","msg":"所以咪話點解咁多人講鐘意，完全唔撚明"},{"pid":"ff58e989e936b5977d26754d63b4a6158770fdf7","tid":2252973,"uid":151501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T02:39:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"373b057449d54c7eedd1a53b1efab42718a15203","tid":2252973,"uid":184233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T02:45:15.000Z","msg":"鍾意香港叫雞方便 <br />\n其他地方就算方便都屌唔到咁多港女 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我愛香港雞 不要北菇雞 !"},{"pid":"e5d942738c836567e131fc5a8f2ec843f72edf56","tid":2252973,"uid":32768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r